ivardefs.name: category
ivardefs.desc: High level categorization, e.g. polymer or nucleic acid, or food, chemical, biological.

ivardefs.name: code_
ivardefs.desc: Codes associated with the substance.

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: Textual description of the substance.

ivardefs.name: domain
ivardefs.desc: If the substance applies to only human or veterinary use.

ivardefs.name: identifier
ivardefs.desc: Identifier by which this substance is known.

ivardefs.name: manufacturer_
ivardefs.desc: A company that makes this substance.

ivardefs.name: moiety_
ivardefs.desc: Moiety, for structural modifications.

ivardefs.name: name_
ivardefs.desc: Names applicable to this substance.

ivardefs.name: note_
ivardefs.desc: Textual comment about this record of a substance.

ivardefs.name: nucleicAcid
ivardefs.desc: Data items specific to nucleic acids.

ivardefs.name: polymer
ivardefs.desc: Data items specific to polymers.

ivardefs.name: property_
ivardefs.desc: General specifications for this substance, including how it is related to other substances.

ivardefs.name: protein
ivardefs.desc: Data items specific to proteins.

ivardefs.name: referenceInformation
ivardefs.desc: General information detailing this substance.

ivardefs.name: relationship_
ivardefs.desc: A link between this substance and another, with details of the relationship.

ivardefs.name: sourceMaterial
ivardefs.desc: Material or taxonomic/anatomical source for the substance.

ivardefs.name: source_
ivardefs.desc: Supporting literature.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: Status of substance within the catalogue e.g. approved.

ivardefs.name: structure
ivardefs.desc: Structural information.

ivardefs.name: supplier_
ivardefs.desc: A company that supplies this substance.

properties.desc: The detailed description of a substance, typically at a level beyond what is used for prescribing.
